title: Genome Sequence of the Novel Reassortant Mammalian Orthoreovirus Strain MRV00304/13, Isolated from a Calf with Diarrhea from the United States
body: The complete genome sequence of MRV1 strain MRV00304/13 has been deposited in GenBank under accession no. KJ676379 (L1), KJ676380 (L2), KJ676381 (L3), KJ676382 (M1), KJ676383 (M2), KJ676384 (M3), KJ676385 (S1), KJ676386 (S2), KJ676387 (S3), and KJ676388 (S4).
